Package Project

Class ProjectController

java.lang.Object
Project.ProjectController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProjectControllerInterface
public class ProjectController extends Object implements ProjectControllerInterface
Manages the interactions and operations related to projects, including displaying dashboards, applying for flats, managing officers, and updating project details.
